  "title": "Pre-school Assistant Teacher",
  "description": "<h4><strong>Job Description</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist class teacher in routine care, classroom management and preparations</li>\n  <li>Classroom management and active communication with parents</li>\n  <li>Ensure safety and hygiene of the children</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least a Fundemental Certificate in Early Childhood</li>\n  <li>1 year of relevant experience in childcare/preschool.</li>\n  <li>Able to commit 5 days/ week, 8am to 5pm</li>\n  <li>Have a passion in teaching young children.</li>\n  <li>Candidate without experience are welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Type: Full-time</p>\n<p>Location: 336 River Valley Road</p>\n<p>Monthly Salary: $2400 - $2600(Full Day)</p>",
